        >
        <Paragraph>
          Paws for Rivers is not responsible for any damages arising from the
          use of our website or products. We do not guarantee that our website
          will always be available or free from errors.
        </Paragraph>
        <Heading size="xs" fontweight="bold" fontstyle="sans" class="mb-4"
          >5. Third-Party Links</Heading
        >
        <Paragraph>
          Our website may contain links to third-party sites. We are not
          responsible for their content, privacy policies, or business
          practices.
        </Paragraph>
        <Heading size="xs" fontweight="bold" fontstyle="sans" class="mb-4"
          >6. Privacy Policy</Heading
        >
        <Paragraph>
          Your use of this website is also governed by our Privacy Policy.
          Please review it for details on how we handle your personal data.
        </Paragraph>
        <Heading size="xs" fontweight="bold" fontstyle="sans" class="mb-4"
          >7. Changes to These Terms</Heading
        >
        <Paragraph>
          We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of our website
          after updates means you accept the revised Terms.
        </Paragraph>
        <Heading size="xs" fontweight="bold" fontstyle="sans" class="mb-4"
          >8. Contact Information</Heading
        >
        <Paragraph>
          For questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a
            class="link link-hover"
            href="mailto:mail@pawsforrivers.com">mail@pawsforrivers.com</a
          >.
        </Paragraph>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </div>
</Layout>
